				<p class="nyt-article-byline">By AARON M. KESSLER</p>
				<p class="nyt-article-summary">Timothy F. Geithner, the former Treasury secretary, was a witness in the trial of a lawsuit over the departmentâs role in the bailout of A.I.G. His book was under scrutiny, too.</p>
			</div>
			
